The [[Star of Aga-Pelar]] was a huge midnight black [[star sapphire]] with an inner asterism of pure white.{{cite book/Desert of Desolation|39}}

The [[Star of Mo-Pelar]] was a fist-sized [[opal]]. 

The [[Star of Khan-Pelar]] was an enormous [[quartz|clear crystal]].

The [[Star of Shah-Pelar]] was a huge faceted [[ruby]].{{cite book/Desert of Desolation|84}}

The [[Star of Melos-Pelar]] was a fist-sized, faceted [[amethyst]] of the deepest purple. It was said to be the shape of either a ball,{{cite book/Desert of Desolation|107}} or an egg.
